dcterms:description: A large cohort of chest radiographs consisting of N = 193,311 frontal CXR images of 54,176 patients, all manually labeled by radiologists. The available labels include pleural effusion, pneumonic infiltrates, and atelectasis, among others.
dcterms:title: UKA-CXR

dcterms:description: An in-house dataset of 1,625 abdominal CT scans from unique, consecutive patients, of which 867 suffered from pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma (PDAC) and 758 were a control group without a tumor.
